Metorex Extends Decline After Vale Says Won’t Amend Bid for the Company

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-11T07:10:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/metorex-extends-decline-after-vale-says-won-t-amend-bid-for-the-company.html
Metorex Ltd. (MTX)  extended declines after
saying it received a letter from Vale SA that the Brazilian
company won’t amend its bid for the South African copper
producer.  The stock snapped two days of increases, retreating 23
cents, or 2.7 percent, to 8.45 rand by 9:07 a.m. in
Johannesburg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  